trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when you use the <see cref="M:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject.Disconnect" /> method of a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject" /> that is not bound to data.
trans-unit.target: 使用未绑定到数据的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject" /> 的 <see cref="M:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject.Disconnect" /> 方法时引发的异常。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject.Disconnect%2A> method removes the data binding from a <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject>.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObjectNotDataBoundException" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObjectNotDataBoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The exception that is the cause of the current exception.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObjectNotDataBoundException" /> class with the inner exception that is the cause of this exception.
trans-unit.target: 使用导致此异常的内部异常初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObjectNotDataBoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the error.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObjectNotDataBoundException" /> class with a specified error message.
trans-unit.target: 用指定的错误消息初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObjectNotDataBoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the error.
The exception that is the cause of the current exception.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObjectNotDataBoundException" /> class with a specified error message and a reference to the inner exception that is the cause of this exception.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的错误消息和对作为此异常原因的内部异常的引用来初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObjectNotDataBoundException" /> 类的新实例。
